sequenceDiagram
    participant Att as Attacker
    participant GW as API Gateway
    participant BE as Backend Service

    Att->>GW: Valid request (normal path)
    GW->>BE: Forward with trusted headers

    Att->>BE: Direct request + forged X-Role: admin
    BE-->>Att: Privileged response (if boundary is weak)

    Note over BE: Mitigated: reject unless trusted caller identity is verified
